                </li>
                <li>Espresso is more than just a drink; it has the power to bring people together and create moments of joy and connection.
                </li>
                <li>Espresso Emporium aims to be a valuable resource for both seasoned espresso drinkers and those just starting out on their espresso journey.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>

